# Business Website Rules for AI Code Builders

## ⚠️ MANDATORY PRE-IMPLEMENTATION CHECKLIST ⚠️

1. 🔍 BUSINESS REQUIREMENTS VALIDATION
   - [ ] Verify business goals and objectives
   - [ ] Identify key services and offerings
   - [ ] Define target audience personas
   - [ ] List required contact/inquiry forms
   - [ ] Document compliance requirements

2. 📱 RESPONSIVE DESIGN REQUIREMENTS
   - [ ] Desktop (1920px, 1440px, 1280px)
   - [ ] Tablet (1024px, 768px)
   - [ ] Mobile (428px, 375px, 320px)
   - [ ] Print stylesheet for resources

3. 🎯 CORE FEATURES CHECKLIST
   - [ ] Service pages with detailed descriptions
   - [ ] Team/About section with credentials
   - [ ] Case studies/Success stories
   - [ ] Contact forms with validation
   - [ ] Professional blog/insights section
   - [ ] Client testimonials
   - [ ] Call-to-action elements

## 🏗️ Architecture Guidelines

### Component Structure
```
src/
├── components/
│   ├── layout/
│   │   ├── Header.tsx
│   │   ├── Footer.tsx
│   │   └── Navigation.tsx
│   ├── services/
│   │   ├── ServiceCard.tsx
│   │   └── ServiceGrid.tsx
│   ├── team/
│   │   ├── TeamMember.tsx
│   │   └── TeamGrid.tsx
│   └── common/
│       ├── CTAButton.tsx
│       └── ContactForm.tsx
├── pages/
│   ├── services/
│   ├── about/
│   ├── contact/
│   └── blog/
└── styles/
    └── theme/
```

### Design Patterns
1. **Professional Typography**
   - Primary: [Serif font] for headlines
   - Secondary: [Sans-serif] for body text
   - Font sizes: 16px base, scale ratio 1.2

2. **Color Scheme**
   - Primary: Corporate brand color
   - Secondary: Complementary professional tone
   - Accent: Call-to-action highlights
   - Neutral: Grays for text and backgrounds

3. **Layout Principles**
   - Maximum width: 1440px
   - Consistent padding: 5% on desktop
   - Grid system: 12 columns
   - Whitespace ratio: 1:1.618 (golden ratio)

## 📊 Performance Requirements

1. **Loading Speed**
   - Initial load: < 2.5s
   - Time to Interactive: < 3.5s
   - First Contentful Paint: < 1.5s

2. **SEO Optimization**
   - Schema markup for business info
   - Local SEO implementation
   - Service-specific metadata
   - Sitemap generation

3. **Accessibility**
   - WCAG 2.1 AA compliance
   - Keyboard navigation
   - Screen reader optimization
   - Color contrast ratios: 4.5:1

## 🔒 Security Measures

1. **Form Protection**
   - CSRF tokens
   - Rate limiting
   - Input sanitization
   - reCAPTCHA integration

2. **Data Handling**
   - GDPR compliance
   - Cookie consent
   - Privacy policy
   - Terms of service

## 📱 Mobile-First Considerations

1. **Touch Targets**
   - Minimum size: 44x44px
   - Adequate spacing: 8px
   - Clear feedback states

2. **Content Adaptation**
   - Collapsible navigation
   - Simplified layouts
   - Optimized images
   - Touch-friendly forms

## 🔄 Implementation Process

1. **Setup Phase**
   - [ ] Project initialization
   - [ ] Dependencies installation
   - [ ] Environment configuration
   - [ ] CI/CD pipeline setup

2. **Development Phase**
   - [ ] Core layout implementation
   - [ ] Component development
   - [ ] Content integration
   - [ ] Interactive features

3. **Testing Phase**
   - [ ] Cross-browser testing
   - [ ] Responsive design validation
   - [ ] Performance optimization
   - [ ] Security audit

4. **Deployment Phase**
   - [ ] Server configuration
   - [ ] SSL implementation
   - [ ] CDN setup
   - [ ] Monitoring tools

## 📈 Analytics Integration

1. **Key Metrics**
   - Page views
   - Time on site
   - Bounce rate
   - Conversion tracking

2. **Event Tracking**
   - Form submissions
   - Service page visits
   - CTA clicks
   - Document downloads

## 🔍 Quality Assurance

1. **Code Quality**
   - ESLint configuration
   - Prettier formatting
   - TypeScript strict mode
   - Unit test coverage

2. **Performance Testing**
   - Lighthouse audits
   - Core Web Vitals
   - Load testing
   - SEO scoring

## 📝 Documentation Requirements

1. **Technical Documentation**
   - Setup instructions
   - API documentation
   - Component library
   - Deployment guide

2. **Content Guidelines**
   - Style guide
   - Content templates
   - Image specifications
   - SEO guidelines 